871
00:45:26,689 --> 00:45:28,189
Respectez le drapeau !

872
00:45:28,190 --> 00:45:30,693
Salut... maintenant !

873
00:45:32,111 --> 00:45:33,445
Et si le chocolat fond ?

874
00:45:33,446 --> 00:45:34,196
Chocolat?

875
00:45:34,447 --> 00:45:35,364
